data.description: Beautiful Country Creek Condos is minutes from Downtown Dallas giving you the best of both worlds – city living with peace & quiet in a 2-story end unit condo. Enter a beautiful, relaxing private courtyard with outdoor carpet & two storage sheds with lockable doors for added security. Well maintained, updated unit with 2-bedrooms & walk-in closets plus upgraded bathrooms adjacent to. Kitchen bar top counter overlooking sink accommodates bar stools. Patio & both bedroom windows have blinds & lighted remote controlled ceiling fans. Downstairs bedroom is currently being used as a work-from-home office. Also, in-unit laundry space with washer-dryer plus shelf storage. Appliances remain with the property. Also features doored entrance to attic with carpeted space for hobbies plus storage. This one is move in ready. Buyer-Agent to verify all information.
